Packages
Package
Description
controllers
The controllers package contains classes that manage the application's control flow.
dao
The dao package contains Data Access Object (DAO) classes responsible for interacting with the underlying data storage and performing CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations.
enums
The enums package contains Java enumerations that represent a set of named constants.
interfaces.dao
The interfaces.dao package contains interfaces that define data access operations.
interfaces.services
The interface.services contains service interfaces defining various functionalities.
interfaces.views
The interfaces.views contains view interfaces defining the user interface functionalities.
main
The main package contains the entry point and core components of the SC2002_CAMs application.
models
The models package contains the data models used in the SC2002_CAMs application.
services
The services package contains classes that provide various services and functionalities for the SC2002_CAMs application.
utils
The utils package contains utility classes that offer general-purpose functions and tools for the SC2002_CAMs application.
views
The views package contains classes that provide various output for the SC2002_CAMs application.
